memory: write_once вҶ’ consistency(cheap)
builtins: {range_check, pedersen, ecdsa, bitwise} вҶ’ efficient(precomputed)

Cairo 0: constraint-oriented (hard)
Cairo 1: Rust-like (easier) вҶ’ same proving model
